---
title: Indian Chicken, Chickpea & Baby Broccoli Curry with Garlic Rice & Roasted Almonds
description: Enjoy a bowl of creamy and rich Indian curry, loaded with colourful veggies and aromatic spices. With a sprinkling of roasted cashews to finish it all off, this delicious meal will beat your local takeaway joint!

*We’ve replaced the cashews in this recipe with roasted almonds due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
